{"tid":677132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[異度空間] 日本列車撞到學生 人卻憑空消失...","createTime":"2018-05-25T02:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T16:05:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":237,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"834a2992f3f12e31500f98eb7a1c4cf1c851e35e","tid":677132,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%81%AD%E9%9B%BB%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E6%93%8A-%E7%AB%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%AD%A4-%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%93%E8%92%B8%E7%99%BC-141514478.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2592%259E%25E6%2593%258A-%25E7%25AB%259F%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25AD%25A4-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%2592%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC-141514478.html&d=IzNnsw2NHj6Y0EKC5Yge5TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f88113a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%81%AD%E9%9B%BB%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E6%93%8A-%E7%AB%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%AD%A4-%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%93%E8%92%B8%E7%99%BC-141514478.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本近日發生一起詭異事故，一名男學生疑似遭到JR列車撞到，而車站調閱監視器後也發現確實有撞到人，但工作人員在現場卻完全沒有發現這名男同學，就連月台、附近醫院都沒有查詢到男同學的蹤跡，憑空消失的怪事連警方也傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Tn7LdYlg2xJzp6g4NHhoCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/4bb90bc25905376b86372cfd75bf2861\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTn7LdYlg2xJzp6g4NHhoCw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F4bb90bc25905376b86372cfd75bf2861&h=6a75b7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《IBC岩手放送》報導，位於岩手縣的JR北上站於23日早上6時許，向警方通報有電車撞到學生的事故，警方調閱監視器後，確實發現有一名身穿校服的男子，遭到電車擦撞，然而警方既沒有在月台發現男同學蹤影，也沒有接獲任何受傷的通報，就連醫院也沒有記錄。<br />\n<br />\n而這起「憑空消失」的擦撞事故，也影響了JR東北本線、北上線的電車停駛約1小時，警方雖然已將男子消失及擦撞事故列案調查，但日本網友紛紛表示「穿越時空了嗎」、「有制服的話，應該可以向學校查證吧」、「先公開監視器畫面再說」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/s7l7SB8QGnVbWNllJmKGgg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/08857e923304ecc9a28fcbd6cd4da89b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fs7l7SB8QGnVbWNllJmKGgg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F08857e923304ecc9a28fcbd6cd4da89b&h=0754fd77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AEG_a.P8GNtHE8AJpxZETg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/eaa61d834ffc664ba5f223879b35baa0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAEG_a.P8GNtHE8AJpxZETg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Feaa61d834ffc664ba5f223879b35baa0&h=1e6e0137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ciw4zyEawfsVXei3eWNcwg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/c1d82d1061bb46c67541a40e07f1ad69\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fciw4zyEawfsVXei3eWNcwg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fc1d82d1061bb46c67541a40e07f1ad69&h=ecd31c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab5fec22cc708188b8ecc08940f3fef220978f9","tid":677132,"uid":26773,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"Jump"},{"pid":"f2b670525e6a38d280e80d7e1ee40ba44753e546","tid":677132,"uid":37005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:50:26.000Z","msg